_note: Nordic Empress / Empress of the Seas (1990-2020) - Originally built as Future Seas for Admiral Cruise Lines, became Royal Caribbean's first short-cruise ship. Renamed Empress of the Seas in 2004, sold to Cordelia Cruises (India) in 2020. If you have videos of this pioneering vessel, please suggest them! Looking for: ship tours, deck walkthroughs, dining, entertainment, stateroom tours, or historical documentaries.
